### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks

### Get task by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/task/123456789

### Create new task
POST http://localhost:3000/task
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "description": "Write and submit the project proposal for the new client"
}

### Update task by ID
PATCH http://localhost:3000/task/123456789
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "completed": true,
}

### Delete task by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/task/123456789